<div data-admin-page="maps">
    <div class="d-flex justify-content-between align-items-center mb-3">
        <header class="mt-3">
            <h4 class="display-6">Mappe</h4>
            <h6>Gestione mappe, anteprima e modalita di visualizzazione dei luoghi</h6>
        </header>
        <div class="d-flex gap-2">
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-primary" data-action="admin-maps-reload">
                <i class="bi bi-arrow-clockwise me-1"></i>Aggiorna
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-primary" data-action="admin-maps-create">
                <i class="bi bi-plus-lg me-1"></i>Nuova mappa
            </button>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="alert alert-info small mb-3">
        L'immagine mappa viene usata come anteprima card. La vista interna dei luoghi dipende dalla modalita:
        scegli <b>Griglia</b> per posizionamento a celle o <b>Visuale</b> per coordinate libere.
    </div>

    <div class="card mb-3">
        <div class="card-body">
            <form id="admin-maps-filters" class="row g-2 align-items-end" autocomplete="off" novalidate>
                <div class="col-auto">
                    <label class="form-label mb-1" for="admin-maps-filter-name">Nome</label>
                    <input type="search" id="admin-maps-filter-name" name="name" class="form-control form-control-sm" placeholder="Nome mappa...">
                </div>
                <div class="col-auto">
                    <label class="form-label mb-1" for="admin-maps-filter-render-mode">Modalita</label>
                    <select id="admin-maps-filter-render-mode" name="render_mode" class="form-select form-select-sm">
                        <option value="">Tutte</option>
                        <option value="grid">Griglia</option>
                        <option value="visual">Visuale</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="col-auto">
                    <label class="form-label mb-1" for="admin-maps-filter-initial">Iniziale</label>
                    <select id="admin-maps-filter-initial" name="initial" class="form-select form-select-sm">
                        <option value="">Tutte</option>
                        <option value="1">Si</option>
                        <option value="0">No</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="col-auto">
                    <label class="form-label mb-1" for="admin-maps-filter-mobile">Mobile</label>
                    <select id="admin-maps-filter-mobile" name="mobile" class="form-select form-select-sm">
                        <option value="">Tutte</option>
                        <option value="1">Si</option>
                        <option value="0">No</option>
                    </select>
                </div>
                <div class="col-auto d-flex align-items-end">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-secondary" data-action="admin-maps-filters-reset">
                        <i class="bi bi-x-circle me-1"></i>Reset
                    </button>
                </div>
            </form>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="grid-admin-maps"></div>

    {% include 'admin/modals/maps.twig' %}
</div>

